parameters: How did you get this far?。
From here on out, the rock is so hard that we'll need a golden pickaxe made of alloy.。
Endurance is the same as the last pickaxe, 25 mining cycles.。
Because sometimes you can find the same pickaxe in the wall.
You can keep digging until you use it all up.。
The endlessly digging magic pickaxe won't work here.。
If we strengthen it further, it will destroy the ore, so we have no choice.。
Of course, the benefit of reducing lava damage to 1 is gone, too.
The golden pickaxes are 30,000 Gs each, wanna play?
If we lose the pickaxe on this floor
You can come back for more.。
